        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued June 15 at 3:37AM CDT until June 15 at 3:45AM CDT by NWS Amarillo TX</headline>
        <description>At 337 AM CDT, severe thunderstorms were located along a line
extending from 6 miles east of Hardesty to 9 miles northwest of
Gruver, moving southeast at 40 mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts and quarter size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor damage to roofs, siding, and trees is possible. Hail
damage to vehicles is expected.

Locations impacted include...
Hardesty, Gruver, Hooker, and Adams.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
